Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.29,0:01:30.81,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請於下載24小時後刪除 如喜歡本作品請支持正版
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.29,0:01:30.81,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻譯:夢の旅人 後期.校正:依戀緋鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.64,0:01:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.22,0:02:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 好不容易回來了卻不上學 整天呆在家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.21,0:02:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了 我自己會收拾 你出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.26,0:02:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.63,0:02:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了 對不起 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.73,0:02:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.35,0:02:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小袋說今晚舉行一個集會 你意下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.48,0:02:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.77,0:02:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這的確讓人不知所措
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.85,0:02:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 我們先在車站會合
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 鶴見同學好像完全沒學乖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一臉松雪只屬於自己的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.97,0:02:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身高181cm 體重68kg 喜歡的食物是八橋煎餅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.41,0:03:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,興趣是女裝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.94,0:03:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女裝?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.76,0:03:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等一下 鶴見 我們的話還沒說完
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.97,0:03:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.81,0:03:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有必要把那個說出來嗎 即使是我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.21,0:03:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.69,0:03:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴見…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.84,0:03:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 來吧 動起手來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.29,0:03:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是預祝小芽明天能順利升天的大宴會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝飾也要引人注目才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.33,0:03:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽用紙巾做紙花
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.54,0:03:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你貴為主角為啥還要親自動手做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.83,0:03:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很好玩啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 做得很漂亮啊 小芽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太別在這裡發呆 做一個垃圾箱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.91,0:03:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,垃圾箱?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.08,0:04:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前 我在班裡不被大家當一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能幹些蠢事來恭維大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.44,0:04:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但仁太你們卻把我當作同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.63,0:04:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然到最後我也只能注視著大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能注視著大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小袋?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.71,0:04:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 所以呢 這次由我來全權負責
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.37,0:04:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們給你作個大排場的送行吧 小芽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小袋真體貼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對這個有什麼看法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可能會去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.06,0:04:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子要把我捉弄到什麼地步才滿足
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要到什麼地步…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.56,0:04:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.58,0:04:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小聰 為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.42,0:04:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 你知道我身高是多少嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.47,0:04:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這一年裡我長高了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.05,0:05:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來都很寂寞啊 無論是聰志還是你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.70,0:05:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘記芽衣子是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用勉強自己去忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過 我希望這份寂寞能大家一同分擔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.36,0:05:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 聰志 還有我 三個人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.46,0:05:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後會怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放出煙花的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.99,0:05:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果小芽就此消失會怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前我一直在想這個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽消失了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.71,0:05:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就能成為跟仁太關係最好的一個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但事實並非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.34,0:06:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果小芽真的不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.85,0:06:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟仁太的距離只會越來越遠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.67,0:06:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然 最近我們的距離有所拉近
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.01,0:06:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是因為小芽回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.28,0:06:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真值得慶幸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.71,0:06:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.57,0:06:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鶴見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.02,0:06:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要去秘密基地嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.73,0:06:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在跟安城一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.13,0:06:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.51,0:06:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.03,0:06:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.12,0:06:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前還幹勁十足地說要讓她升天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了關鍵時候就害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.77,0:06:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很可悲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.41,0:06:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因害怕而避開小芽 跟安城在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只想讓自己覺得悲慘的不止自己一個對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.17,0:07:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想起來了 小芽打電話叫我出去時所說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.25,0:07:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時她說想為仁太做點什麼希望我們能幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.00,0:07:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 雪集 鶴子她說什麼了 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.47,0:07:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事相求
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳴 這是只有你才能辦到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼他們不來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.73,0:07:33.13,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（小芽再見）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.14,0:07:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦 反正明天還會見面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該開始了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.59,0:07:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去叫他們來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.03,0:07:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 喂 小袋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.91,0:07:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.28,0:07:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.70,0:07:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我買來了一些零食
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.24,0:07:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是鶴子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.82,0:07:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.12,0:07:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集我愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.05,0:07:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 要舉行晚會了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.11,0:07:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你們好久了 我相信你們一定會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:07:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的好高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.65,0:08:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 我超喜歡吃這個的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.34,0:08:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家到齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺漸漸接近終點了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在小芽與我等組成超和平BUSTERS的這個地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.67,0:08:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開場白就免了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.05,0:08:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 請主角小芽上前發言
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:28.52,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（感謝大家今天為小芽做的一切）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.01,0:08:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:32.13,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（小芽明天就要升天了）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.19,0:08:41.60,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（我想跟大家和睦相處直到最後 請多多關照）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.37,0:08:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上是小芽的發言
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.54,0:08:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽 你要吃這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顏色鮮紅一片 一定好辣的 我不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.81,0:09:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好辣是這樣寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.90,0:09:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不辣 沒事的 就嘗一口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別 別塞進我嘴裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.92,0:09:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼餘興節目嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.83,0:09:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去只不過是個酒會而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.07,0:09:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是個集會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.95,0:09:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得一次機會 我們玩點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.07,0:09:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.13,0:09:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有什麼餘興節目可玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.30,0:09:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.08,0:09:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再做一次那天的那件事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.90,0:09:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重現那天在這裡發生的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.52,0:09:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡發生的事情是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.54,0:09:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.44,0:09:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.59,0:09:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做這種事情到底有什麼意義
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.96,0:09:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.65,0:09:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁…仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.12,0:09:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡小芽對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:09:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快說吧 小芽也在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.96,0:10:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.90,0:10:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…是 不是 不是 不是 不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.41,0:10:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 為什麼要舊事重提
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.04,0:10:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡小芽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡逃跑的話不就跟那時候一樣嗎 仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.93,0:11:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽默不作聲 只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.21,0:11:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刷刷的落下眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.17,0:11:03.85,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十話 煙花
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.25,0:11:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你別再哭了 太不像樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.54,0:11:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我就是不像樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.66,0:11:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是雪集事先安排的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.21,0:11:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那個 我說還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說 那天他的答案是不言而喻的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.03,0:11:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到小芽升天了 事情都還沒弄清楚 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在迷惘不安中繼續輸給本應不復存在的小芽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.64,0:11:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得這樣也無所謂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.30,0:11:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴子你根本不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.62,0:11:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被心上人永遠拒絕的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.46,0:11:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我一直喜歡著雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.68,0:12:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集他一直追趕著小芽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.46,0:12:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我一直看著他追趕的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.81,0:12:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴子…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.90,0:12:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠什麼的誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.18,0:12:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽升天的話 宿海也許會…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.37,0:12:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  雪集他就絕對不會選擇我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.28,0:12:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為即使小芽升天了他還能找到替身 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.36,0:12:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而那替身就是你 安城
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.75,0:12:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 不是這樣的 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.59,0:12:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集從來沒想過找我當替身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.59,0:12:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有我 就算有多痛苦也不會跟雪集交往
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我喜歡的是仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.63,0:12:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別人怎可能替代得了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.66,0:12:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 正因為無可替代 才必須讓小芽升天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.33,0:13:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太 對不起 我做出了那麼荒唐的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.41,0:13:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小袋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.59,0:13:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那時候 我感覺一切好像回到了從前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到從前…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.93,0:13:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 剛才你說的話是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.81,0:13:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.37,0:13:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽也喜歡仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.10,0:13:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的喜歡可不單是作為朋友的喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.78,0:13:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.07,0:13:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想娶我為妻的喜歡對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.16,0:13:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果小芽能普通地長大的話 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.22,0:13:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道能否成為仁太的新娘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不是普通…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.98,0:13:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要升天 一直留在這裡不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.63,0:14:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.71,0:14:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會升天的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.44,0:14:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為呢 我想要投胎轉世 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不升天的話是辦不到的 也不能跟大家好好聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.66,0:14:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟大家…好好聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.46,0:14:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 小芽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.38,0:14:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太說喜歡你 你的回答是什麼 不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.14,0:14:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時她說想為仁太做點什麼希望我們能幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.48,0:14:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.59,0:14:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡小芽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明早就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.02,0:15:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓你升天吧 好嗎 小芽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只跟我一起不行嗎 小芽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.37,0:15:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 小芽 你知道投胎轉世嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.72,0:15:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投胎轉世?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.33,0:15:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 即使生命走到了盡頭 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.91,0:15:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會變成嬰兒重新降生到世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.22,0:15:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止是人類 也許小貓咪和花兒也是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.27,0:15:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 生命的凋零一點也不悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.28,0:16:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.21,0:16:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 只有一點 只有一點令人傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨 請再等一下 我跟大家一起給你放煙花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.81,0:16:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以請再等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.57,0:16:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 首先是裝好必要的部件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:16:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.36,0:17:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.57,0:17:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.24,0:17:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴子看起來跟小時候一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉換心情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.81,0:17:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.84,0:17:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.11,0:17:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太 你拿著那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.13,0:17:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預備
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.74,0:17:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.93,0:17:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.75,0:17:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.01,0:17:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.31,0:17:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好像聞到股似曾相識的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.53,0:17:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是仁太叫小聰來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.82,0:17:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.49,0:17:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.94,0:17:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.46,0:18:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要 結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.26,0:18:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預備
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.79,0:18:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.62,0:18:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為小芽跟我們的利害關係是一致的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會讓你升天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.45,0:18:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 現在的話還能夠阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.55,0:18:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.74,0:18:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽一定會很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.18,0:18:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會讓你阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.08,0:18:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的話還能夠阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.40,0:18:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能夠阻止 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.82,0:18:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要升天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.24,0:18:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小聰力氣很大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.12,0:19:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 剩下就是發射了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.07,0:19:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.85,0:19:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 有什麼要說的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.54,0:19:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家弟弟在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.49,0:19:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那我自說自話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.88,0:19:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興 一直以來謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.84,0:19:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小袋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.65,0:19:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 仁太也說一句
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.83,0:19:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.43,0:19:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太晚的話會打擾到近鄰的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.03,0:19:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.97,0:19:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係嗎 現在的話還能夠阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.04,0:20:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能夠阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.96,0:20:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.59,0:20:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙花…發射了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.03,0:21:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 天空開出一朵花來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.54,0:21:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…芽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.02,0:21:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在嗎 我問你 她還在嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.11,0:21:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 宿海 仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.71,0:21:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 小芽 那時候我在想  
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.61,0:21:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒消失真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.60,0:22:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太他最近…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
